<br>
There was another thread about using pet's in Hate or not.. for me personally, I really want my Apothic, so am willing to put up with a no pet rule for the duration, and i general feel quite useful even without a pet in a raid situation, even though i would rather be using one. So your call completely.. for me, if there is a chance of me getting something nice, i'll put up with just about anything. <br>
